section_label: Three images showing different views of the proper
raw_md_fragment:
[IMAGE]
Three images showing different views of the property:
1. A side view of the building showing a narrow alleyway between buildings.
1. A rear view showing a parking area with several cars parked.
1. A close-up of the building's utility meters mounted on the exterior brick wall.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image showing a stairwell with brick walls and mailboxes on the right side. The stairwell has a metal railing and carpeted steps.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a door at the end of a hallway with a painting on the wall to the left. The hallway has a metal railing and carpeted floor.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a brick building exterior with a red awning above the entrance door. The building has multiple windows with air conditioning units.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a stairwell with a painting on the wall and a metal railing. The steps are carpeted.
[/IMAGE]
